# Normalize line endings to LF in the working tree on every platform (including
# Windows), so builds and tests see the same bytes everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# The vendored Asciidoctor stylesheet is embedded verbatim via `include_str!`
# and compared byte-for-byte against Asciidoctor's LF output. Keep it LF on all
# platforms — a CRLF checkout would embed `\r\n` and diverge from Asciidoctor.
*.css text eol=lf
